  <p align="left"> 
  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="2"><a name="4"><font color="gold">Enchanter</font></a><br>
    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">The primary focus of the Enchanter’s art 
        can be summed up by the name of the arcane order to which he belongs: 
        Enchanter. Their spells are crafted to enchant people, places, and things. 
        This art allows them to charm beings and make them fight for their new 
        master, or magically enhance the capabilities of a sword. They also have 
        some skill in offensive spells, but are never as skilled as a Wizard.</font></p>
      
