    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">Paladins are the very picture of a holy 
        knight, fighting for the cause of good in all aspects of his life. They 
        share some of the power of a Cleric and a good deal of the fighting ability 
        of a Warrior but have a few powers all their own.</font></p>
      
