  <p align="left"> 
  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="2"><a name="9"><font color="gold">Ranger</font></a><br>
    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">The Ranger is a meld between a Warrior 
        and a Druid, sharing some of the skills of both. They are at home in the 
        outdoors.</font></p>
      
    <p><font face="verdana" size="2"><img src="assets/interface/dot.gif" width="8" height="8"> 
      <a href="default.asp?dest=class/ranger">Ranger Creation/Play Guide</a><br>
