    Knight </font></a><br>
    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">The evil twin to the Paladin class, Shadow 
        Knights derive all of their powers from the evil gods whom they serve. 
        They are a meld of Warrior and Necromancer and share some of their abilities 
        and spells.</font></p>
      
