    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">They are similar to the Cleric, but are 
        more of a tribal witch doctor and are typically found amongst the more 
        primitve races. Their primary focus is largely healing and other Clerical 
        type spells, but they also have a good deal of offensive spells.</font></p>
      
