  <p align="left"> 
  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="2"><a name="13"><font color="gold">Warrior</font></a><br>
    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">Warriors are the masters of armed combat 
        in all its many forms. They are at home on the battlefield and are trained 
        to take punishment as much as dole it out, so their Hit Points are the 
        highest of any class.</font></p>
      
    <p><font face="verdana" size="2"><img src="assets/interface/dot.gif" width="8" height="8"> 
      <a href="default.asp?dest=class/warrior">Warrior Creation Guide</a><br>
