  <p align="left"><font face="verdana" size="2"><a name="14"><font color="gold">Wizard</font></a><br>
    <br>
    </font>
  <div align="left"> 
    <blockquote> 
      <p><font face="verdana" size="2">Wizards are the master seekers of knowledge, 
        and their talents and spells are focused on this goal. They use powerful 
        spells to not only see things from afar but to transport them there as 
        well. This thirst for arcane knowledge has also made them the true masters 
        of the strongest form of defense: offensive spells of pure destruction. 
        In their ability to do magical damage, they have no rivals.</font></p>
      
